      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/jana-partners-signs-up-sixth-executive-it-pushes-changes-lamb-weston-filing-2024-12-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五提交的监管文件显示，Jana Partners 正在与第六位高管合作，推动 Lamb Weston 进行变革，这表明这位激进投资者可能寻求更换这家炸薯条制造商董事会的大多数成员。]]></description>
