      <title>泰森食品等家禽加工企业将支付 1.8 亿美元以解决工人的工资索赔</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/tyson-other-poultry-processors-pay-180-million-settle-workers-wage-claims-2024-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品和其他八家家禽加工商已同意支付 1.8 亿美元，以解决美国法院指控他们合谋压低家禽工人工资的诉讼，该协议使得该案的总和解金额达到近 4 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/tyson-other-poultry-processors-pay-180-million-settle-workers-wage-claims-2024-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 16:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
