      <title>美联储根据法律裁决对银行压力测试提出重大修改</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/fed-announces-changes-bank-stress-tests-boost-transparency-trim-volatility-2024-12-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦储备委员会周一表示，鉴于最近的法律发展，它正考虑对其年度银行“压力测试”进行重大修改，包括允许银行对其使用的模型发表评论，这是华尔街银行的重大胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/fed-announces-changes-bank-stress-tests-boost-transparency-trim-volatility-2024-12-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 21:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前法官结束了针对 Hagens Berman 律师事务所的制药费用裁决诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/ex-judge-ends-lawsuit-against-law-firm-hagens-berman-over-pharma-fee-award-2024-12-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位前联邦法官兼一家制药公司的董事撤回了他的诉讼，该诉讼指控全国原告律师事务所 Hagens Berman Sobol Shapiro 未能向他支付在起诉制药商惠氏的诉讼中应得的律师费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/ex-judge-ends-lawsuit-against-law-firm-hagens-berman-over-pharma-fee-award-2024-12-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 17:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
