    <item>
      <title>凯勒·波兹曼放弃诉讼后，Tubi 大规模仲裁将继续推进</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/legalindustry/tubi-mass-arbitration-move-forward-after-keller-postman-drops-lawsuit-2024-12-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[律师事务所凯勒波斯特 (Keller Postman) 撤销了在洛杉矶对流媒体视频网站 Tubi 提起的诉讼，该诉讼指控该网站存在诉讼不当行为，双方互相指责 Tubi 歧视其用户，并且凯勒波斯特向 Tubi 提出了毫无根据的大规模仲裁索赔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/legalindustry/tubi-mass-arbitration-move-forward-after-keller-postman-drops-lawsuit-2024-12-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 22:58:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
